//Mediastinal vessels - Vena cava

Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 09 of Cardio MRI
And I select 'Finding' radio button
And I select 'Mediastinal vessels' from the dropdown menu

When I select 'Vena cava' radio button
Then 'Superior' radio button is enabled
And 'Inferior' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Superior' radio button
Then 'Persistent VCS left' radio button is enabled
And 'Mirror-inverted VCS' radio button is enabled
And 'Retroaortic V. brachiocephalica left' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Inferior' radio button
Then 'Left VCI' radio button is enabled
And 'Doubled VCI' radio button is enabled
